name: Drop!
Lore: 'Anakin had to heed Qui-Gon''s advice to avoid the rapidly approaching storm.',
Text: 'Use 3 Force to deploy on table. During your move phase, if opponent has 13 or more cards in hand, you may use 4 Force to place all but 8 (random choice) in Used Pile. Once during any control phase, you may place up to three cards from hand in Used Pile.',
